<i>noun</i>: 포장 [포장], 치장 [치장], 장식 [장식], 수식 [수식], 단장 [단장], 꾸밈새 [꾸밈새] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>포장 [포장]</dt><br>
<dd>1. wrapping; gift-wrapping; package; packaging material</dd><br>
<dd>물건을 싸거나 꾸림. 또는 싸거나 꾸리는 데 사용하는 재료.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of wrapping or packing an object; or the material used for such a purpose.</dd><br>
<dd>2. decoration; exaggeration</dd><br>
<dd>겉으로만 그럴듯하게 꾸밈.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of making something look or sound good on the surface only.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>치장 [치장]</dt><br>
<dd>decoration; grooming</dd><br>
<dd>잘 매만져 곱게 꾸밈.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of adorning the appearance of someone or something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>장식 [장식]</dt><br>
<dd>decoration</dd><br>
<dd>아름답게 꾸밈. 또는 꾸미는 데 쓰이는 물건.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of decorating something beautifully, or an item used in decorating.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>수식 [수식]</dt><br>
<dd>1. decoration</dd><br>
<dd>겉모양을 꾸밈.</dd><br>
<dd>An adornment of the appearance.</dd><br>
<dd>2. embellishment</dd><br>
<dd>글이나 문장의 표현을 화려하고 기교 있게 꾸밈.</dd><br>
<dd>An embellishment of the expression in a composition or sentence in a fanciful and stylish manner.</dd><br>
<dd>3. modification</dd><br>
<dd>문법에서, 관형어나 부사어 등을 체언이나 용언에 덧붙여 그 뜻을 분명하게 하거나 꾸미는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>A linguistic phenomenon in which an adnominal phrase, adverb, etc., relates to a substantive or a predicate in a sentence by way of specifying its meaning or qualifying it in other ways.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>단장 [단장]</dt><br>
<dd>1. adorning oneself</dd><br>
<dd>얼굴이나 머리, 옷차림 등을 예쁘게 꾸밈.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of making up one's face, grooming hair, and dressing up.</dd><br>
<dd>2. decoration</dd><br>
<dd>건물이나 시설 등을 손질하여 꾸밈.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of repairing and bedecking a building, facility, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>꾸밈새 [꾸밈새]</dt><br>
<dd>decoration; being well-groomed</dd><br>
<dd>꾸민 모양새.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being decorated or well-groomed.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>